  "name": "RPlog_Apprentice_Revealed",
  "title": "Apprentice Revealed",
  "summary": "Aboard the CSA flagship, Colonel Gren Delede secretly brings Luke Skywalker, his wife Twila Virda, and the Chief Medical Officer Xar'on Tanner to the cell of the captured Captain Antoine Dareus. Sensing something amiss as he approaches, Luke discovers that the imprisoned Dareus has awakened the ability to use the Force and now serves as a Sith Apprentice in command of Lord Malign's flagship Predator. Reaching deep into the Force, Luke overpowers Dareus's resistance with a relentless mind compulsion, forcing the Sith to answer truthfully about his role, Malign's organization, and its goal of restoring a Sith Empire. Dareus rages and circles the Jedi, taunting Twila and warning of a coming reckoning, but reveals no concrete plans exist yet. Luke yields the floor to Twila, who orders Dareus heavily sedated for transfer to a Force-user stasis chamber, and Luke leaves the Sith with parting words meant to haunt him as he slips into drugged unconsciousness, vowing revenge.",
